            {
              "id": "3075e00",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Amerigroup International stands at the forefront of the clean energy revolution, delivering unparalleled expertise and turnkey solutions in hydrogen production and dispensing, methanol fuel cell power generation and range extenders, and renewable energy generation with solar, wind turbines, and innovative water solar solutions.</p><p>We also specialize in liquefied natural gas (LNG) infrastructure — including onshore regasification terminals, offshore Floating Storage and Regasification Units (FSRU), and international LNG supply logistics — as well as power grid modernization and power plant integration with new energy technologies around the globe.</p>"
              },
              "elements": []
            }
          ],
          "isInner": false
        },
        {
          "id": "6b79fb7",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
